.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[CR]VTTRegion\f[R] interface\[em]part of the API for handling
WebVTT (text tracks on media presentations)\[em]describes a portion of
the video to render a \f[CR]VTTCue\f[R] onto.
.SH CONSTRUCTOR
.TP
\f[B]VTTRegion()\f[R]
Returns a newly created \f[CR]VTTRegion\f[R] object.
